<div style="text-align: center;"><br>
Welcome to the first edition of the NIWA newsletter!<br>
Since this is our first newsletter, we'd love to hear your feedback <a href="https://niwa.typeform.com/to/bXFVt4" target="_blank" style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #2BAADF;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;">here</a>.<br>
